name: IntexSoft
tag_list: software-development, outsourcing, offshore, software, it-outsourcing, offshore-software-development, software-outsourcing, programming, technology
overview: IntexSoft is a Belarus-based offshore software development company. It provides such services as business analysis, software architecture design, application development, software testing and maintenance, project management. IntexSoft also offers dedicated team of developers and testers. The company mainly specializes in web applications, enterprise applications, mobile applications development for both startups and SMEs.
